Now each cult star has about 100 followers.
- But several thousand come to the performances of Stas Mikhailov!
- Abandoned women come to him, where the sexual-social sphere plays a role.
For cultural reasons, 300 people come and not 10 thousand, so there is less management, money, and everything perishes.
I have followers, and the most important thing is not to deceive them and not to destroy what has been achieved.
